  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.springframework.beans.factory.Aware, org.springframework.context.ApplicationContextAware, org.springframework.core.Ordered, org.springframework.web.context.ServletContextAware, org.springframework.web.servlet.ViewResolver

    @RefreshScope
 @Component(value="registeredServiceViewResolver")
public class RegisteredServiceThemeBasedViewResolver
extends org.thymeleaf.spring4.view.ThymeleafViewResolver
    RegisteredServiceThemeBasedViewResolver is an alternate Spring View Resolver that utilizes a service's associated theme to selectively choose which set of UI views will be used to generate the standard views.
    Since:
    4.1.0
